      • diffDocuments

        public static DiffInfo diffDocuments(org.w3c.dom.Document newDoc,
                                     org.w3c.dom.Document testDoc)
                              throws org.custommonkey.xmlunit.exceptions.ConfigurationException
        Compares two documents representing file trees and returns data structure with comparison information. Both given documents will remain unchanged. Uses XMLUnit engine (http://xmlunit.sourceforge.net/)
        Parameters:
        testDoc - document representing older file tree
        newDoc - document representing newer file tree
        Returns:
        root of file tree with diff information
        Throws:
        org.custommonkey.xmlunit.exceptions.ConfigurationException
